data.description: ***BACK ON MARKET TO NO FAULT OF SELLERS - SELLERS OFFERING $5,000 IN PAID CLOSING COSTS - can use the $5,000 for buying down interest rate, closing costs, improvements or whatever Buyer wants!! - - This is truly a special property with room to customize to your preferences. Nestled in the heart of Edmond, mature shade trees beckon you to your personal retreat. Situated on more than half an acre, this home has everything for a new or growing family. The large deck overlooks an expansive backyard that backs up to a greenbelt, offering plenty of privacy as well as room to run around, practice sports, or entertain. Inside, multiple levels offer ultimate flexibility for your family’s needs. Filled with an abundance of natural light, the functional layout provides ample opportunity to create your personal haven for family gatherings, watching the big game, or just relaxing in private. The main level consists of 2 living areas, dining room and eat-kitchen overlooking both the backyard and living room. Imagine the perfect spot to cook breakfast, enjoy your morning coffee while gazing across the serene backyard, or an ideal space for the kids to do homework before heading outside to play. Downstairs, the lower level boasts another living area, game room, wet bar, bedroom, full bathroom & provides additional access to the backyard. Upstairs, the primary bedroom with full bathroom and walk-in closet, plus 3 additional bedrooms and another full bath, will certainly check all your boxes. Mere minutes away from Edmond Memorial High School, Central Middle School, Rankin YMCA, Pelican Bay and the newly renovated Stephenson Park...this home is just waiting for you to put your personal stamp on it and call it home. Schedule your showing today before it gets away!
